<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqmaps.com/mapz/fearplane2.jpg">www.eqmaps.com/mapz/fearplane2.jpg</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
<br>
This is an aereal view of the plane that will give you a feel for where you will be running through.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqmaps.com/mapz/fearplane5.jpg">www.eqmaps.com/mapz/fearplane5.jpg</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
  The safe spot if you have your back against the north wall will have a large tree immediately on your right and a small tree to your left a bit.  In front of you is an open area with the firewall to the south east and a hill to the south west.   Camp to the immediate east of the large tree. Best thing to do is go in with someone that knows the way.  95% of the time if you go in the night before after the raid has nearly finished or finished there should be no mobs up and you can just run in.  Do NOT go inside the firewall as normally the temple is still full of mobs. <p>Twiggie Tymberwolf
